All lots were surveyed in accordance with law and existing regulations promulgated thereunder, by Cesar E. Trinidad, Geodetic Engineer, on December 5-9, 1934, and was approved on March 5, 1973.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 15th day of May, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and eighty-seven.

(Sgd.) CORAZON C. AQUINO

By the President: (Sgd.) JOKER P. ARROYO Executive Secretary

